-- Lufthansa Cargo Unit Sees 2nd-Best Profit in 2011, Zeitung Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-15T21:22:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/lufthansa-cargo-unit-sees-2nd-best-profit-in-2011-zeitung-says.html
Deutsche Lufthansa AG (LHA) ’s cargo
division will report its second-best earnings this year
following its record performance last year,  Boersen-Zeitung 
reported in a preview of a story that will be published
tomorrow, citing an interview with the unit’s Chief Financial
Officer Peter Gerber.  To contact the reporter on this story:
